com.metsci.glimpse.charts.vector.parser
Class OGRInfo

java.lang.Object
  com.metsci.glimpse.charts.vector.parser.OGRInfo

public class OGRInfo
extends java.lang.Object

The 'Info' suffix on a classname usually indicates that the class is some kind of data only value class. This is not that kind of class. This class is named OGRInfo because it is a wrapper around the ogrinfo, the gdal command line utility. The gdal orginfo dumps out s57 features onto the console. We will invoke that tool via the java RunTime and parse the console output. Ubuntu users, you add ubuntu gis stable package to your source list. The following page has all the goodness. https://launchpad.net/~ubuntugis/+archive/ppa deb http://ppa.launchpad.net/ubuntugis/ppa/ubuntu lucid main deb-src http://ppa.launchpad.net/ubuntugis/ppa/ubuntu lucid main
